  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──Thursday. Morning of the 5th week.\nMy relationship with Nana has deepened, and the treatments are becoming more daring. And fortunately, there are changes in the business situation too..."
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(Already the 5th week... Recently, little by little, new customers have been coming.)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(Yesterday there were 3, the day before 2... Everyone said in unison \"I heard from a friend.\")"
    },
    {
      "include": "common/weekly_settlement"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "Good morning! Please take care of me again today.",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "Good morning, Nana. Actually, I wanted to thank you."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "Thank me... for what?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "Recently, new customers have been increasing. Everyone says \"I heard from a friend,\" so I'm sure you've been promoting the shop for me."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "Oh... yes. When I told my friends, everyone was interested...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "I really like the massages here... so I wanted everyone to experience them too.",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "Thank you so much. Thanks to you, I think I can keep this shop running."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "Oh no... I just talked about it because I thought it was good...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "But... that special outfit was a bit hard to explain...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_006"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "Hahaha, I suppose so. But you seem to have gotten quite used to it."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "Well... I was embarrassed at first, but now I think of it as part of the treatment.",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_007"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "So, how are you feeling today?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "Actually... I feel like my body has become very sensitive lately...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_008"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "Even just a light touch makes me flinch...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_009"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "That's evidence that your blood circulation has improved and your nerves are becoming more active."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "Is that so... but it feels strange...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_010"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "Especially... my chest and stomach area... feel so tingly...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_011"
    },
    {
      "id": "choice_massage5",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "I see... that's evidence your body is changing.",
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "It's a healthy response",
          "trustDelta": 2,
          "developDelta": 0,
          "next": "healthy_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "Your female hormones are activating",
          "trustDelta": 1,
          "developDelta": 1,
          "next": "hormone_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "You might need more development",
          "trustDelta": 0,
          "developDelta": 2,
          "next": "develop_path"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "healthy_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "A healthy response... I see. That's reassuring.",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_012"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "Yes. It's proof your body is functioning properly, so don't worry.",
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "hormone_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "F-female hormones... you mean?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_013"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "Yes. When massage improves blood circulation, hormonal balance is also regulated. It means you're becoming more feminine."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "More feminine... now that you mention it, my skin condition has been improving lately too...",
      "next": "change_clothes",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_014"
    },
    {
      "id": "develop_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "D-development...?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_015"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "Ah, no... I mean increasing your body's sensitivity. Your body still has hidden potential."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "S-saying it like that... is kind of embarrassing...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_016"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "Sorry, sorry. But it means there's room for you to feel even better.",
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "change_clothes",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "Well then, let's get you changed again today."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "Yes. I'm quite used to it now.",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_017"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_closeeyes_closemouth",
      "text": "(But... lately when I put on this outfit, my heart starts racing...)",
      "cutInImage": "nana_changing",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_018"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "I've changed.",
      "outfit": "micro_bikini",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_019"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "(Still a wonderful body...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "Today, I'll give you an especially careful treatment, more than usual."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "Eh... more careful than usual...?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_020"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "Yes. You're a special customer. VIP treatment, you could say."
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "S-special... that's too much...",
      "voiceFile": "story_day5_021"
    },
    {
      "id": "massage_start",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "Well then, let's begin."
    }
  ]
